      <div id="about-box">

       <br />

        <h2>What made you so interested in horses? Do you plan to get any other horses? Are you going to become a pro horse rider when you grow up?</h2>
        <p>I don´t know what made me so interested in horses, it´s difficult for me to answer because it´s all about the horses I like. I started riding when I was 3-years-old and I have been riding ever since. I like the company of the horses, they are so mild and loving if you take good care of them.<br />
It´s really hard to become a pro rider, it costs a lot of money and time and you have to have a really good horse to go all the way and last but not least you have to have a little luck. I wish I had the funds and time for it but I don´t. The closest I have been to pro level has been with my horse Rozolino. Next time we move up it´s for national competitions, I really, really hope that happens.</p>

        <h2>I was wondering what it is like to be so famous and have your own website and all. It must be so cool!</h2>
        <p>I don´t know if I´m famous, I don´t feel famous: I´m still the same old Sara I use to be.<br />
I really like to go to events to meet with all of you. It makes me so happy to see and hear about the girls and boys I meet. It´s kind of strange writing autographs. I don´t think I´ll ever get used to it. I get shy around all that attention.</p>
        
        <h2>Do you believe in magical things such as unicorns roaming the earth during a time before humans came? I do. I mean, some people may think that it's silly to believe in those things but I believe that they once existed.</h2>
        <p>I don´t think you are silly, I also believe in magical things. When I was younger I had a friend who only I could see, it´s important to use your imagination it´s makes the world better!</p>   

